241	/**
242	 * Select the current conference from the decoded document, matching today's
243	 * `getCurrentConference` semantics exactly (CONTEXT.md §"Current Conference"):
244	 * the first conference whose start date is still in the future, falling back to
245	 * the most recent (last) one.
