311	// The corpus asserts `DraftEditor.editDocument(scope, routeOverride(entries))`
312	// produces a draft byte-identical to the oracle's `stored` JSON across every
313	// override shape the route's two override-builders emit: dotted-path leaves,
314	// translation fields (`t:<locale>:<key>` → `collectTranslations`), numeric
